<h1>Daily Plan: Tuesday, December 30, 2025</h1>

<h2>Overview</h2>

<p><strong>Context:</strong> Day 2 of sustainable daily workflow. Complete widget API integration, review Dec 29 audit results, prepare year-end summary of Dec 26-30 work.</p>

<p><strong>Objectives:</strong> 3 Priority Tasks - E.1 Phase 3 widget API integration, audit results review, year-end summary preparation.</p>

<h2>Priority 1: E.1 Phase 3 Widget API Integration</h2>

<p><strong>Objective:</strong> Implement functional API calls from widget to <code>/ai/generate</code> and <code>/ai/chat</code> endpoints.</p>

<ul>
<li>Connect widget send button to API endpoint</li>
<li>Implement message display (render responses in message list)</li>
<li>Add loading indicator during API calls</li>
<li>Handle errors gracefully (show error messages in widget)</li>
<li>Test end-to-end: user input → API call → response display</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Time Estimate:</strong> 2-3 hours</p>

<h2>Priority 2: Review Dec 29 Audit Results & Plan Adjustments</h2>

<p><strong>Objective:</strong> Analyze Dec 29 audit report; adjust plans if needed based on actual progress vs. estimated tasks.</p>

<ul>
<li>Read audit_2025-12-29.md (generated from Daily Audit Agent)</li>
<li>Compare tasks completed vs. estimated; document variances</li>
<li>Check message persistence testing results; update E.1 status accordingly</li>
<li>Review three-agent audit workflow; note improvements for Dec 31+ workflow</li>
<li>Update Dec 30 plan if blockers discovered</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Time Estimate:</strong> 45 mins - 1 hour</p>

<h2>Priority 3: Year-End Summary & Jan 1-4 Plan Preview</h2>

<p><strong>Objective:</strong> Document Dec 26-30 accomplishments; preview work for Jan 1-4 (post-holiday).</p>

<ul>
<li>Create year-end summary document (5-day sprint overview)</li>
<li>Metrics: Plans completed (A.3), Plans in progress (E.1 Phase 3), Architecture designed (F.1)</li>
<li>Code changes summary: 60+ changes across message persistence, JSON parsing, UI/UX</li>
<li>Preview Jan 1-4: E.1 Phase 3 completion, F.1 feature-to-plan mapping implementation, optional A.2 K8s Readiness planning</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Time Estimate:</strong> 45 mins - 1 hour</p>

<h2>Notes</h2>

<ul>
<li><strong>Widget Testing:</strong> Verify credentials: 'include' fix allows cookies to be sent; test in browser DevTools</li>
<li><strong>Audit Review:</strong> If three-agent workflow had issues, document in current_session.md.archivenotused for improvement</li>
<li><strong>Post-Holiday Planning:</strong> Jan 1 is New Year's Day (no work expected); plan resumes Jan 2</li>
</ul>
